title: COMETS program begins in November for girls interested in STEM (Penn State New Kensington)
text: ( Source : Penn State New Kensington ) Fifty-three COMETS students were honored last year during Recognition Night in the Penn State New Kensington Conference Center . 10/20/ 2015 - Eight-month program, Courses on Math , Engineering, Technology
